Package nl.tudelft.dnainator.parser

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EdgeParser
    An interface for parsing edge entries, using the Iterator pattern.
    NodeParser
    An interface for parsing nodes, using the Iterator pattern.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BufferedEdgeParser
    An EdgeParser which uses a BufferedReader as its source.
    BufferedNodeParser
    A NodeParser, which uses a BufferedReader as its source.
    HeaderParser
    Parses the header of a node.
    TreeParser
    This class parses newick files to TreeNode items.
